@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor User

rectangle "App Shell" as Shell {
  rectangle "Dashboard (Home)" as Dash
  rectangle "Transactions" as Tx
  rectangle "Import CSV" as Imp
  rectangle "Categories" as Cat
  rectangle "Rules" as Rules
  rectangle "Accounts" as Acct
}

User --> Dash : Open app (default route)
User --> Tx : Navigate
User --> Imp : Navigate
User --> Cat : Navigate
User --> Rules : Navigate
User --> Acct : Navigate

Dash --> Tx : Click Top Category bar\n(or NeedsReview badge)\n=> open Transactions with filters

note right of Tx
Transactions filters (persisted per session):
- Date range (default this month)
- Account
- Category
- Status (NeedsReview/Reviewed/Ignored)
- Show Transfers toggle
- Include Ignored toggle (default OFF)
end note

Imp --> Tx : Import completed\n=> "View imported transactions"\npre-filter: Imported timestamp window
Rules --> Tx : Re-run rules on selection\n=> results reflected in list
Cat --> Tx : Category renamed\n=> reflected in list + filters
Acct --> Imp : Account selected for import
@enduml
